      %h3 Dependencies

      %p Please note that Netty has <em>no mandatory external dependencies</em>. JDK 1.5 (1.6 for Netty 4+) or above is all that you need to run Netty.

      %h3 Getting notified on a new release

      %p You can either subscribe to <a href="../news/index.html">our official blog</a> or follow <a href="https://twitter.com/netty_project">@netty_project</a> at Twitter.

      %h3 Downloading from the Maven central repository

      %p Add the following dependency section to your <tt>pom.xml</tt>:

      %pre.brush:xml
        :source
          <dependencies>
            ...
            <dependency>
              <groupId>io.netty</groupId>
              <artifactId>netty</artifactId> <!-- Use 'netty-all' for 4.0 or above -->
              <version>X.Y.Z.Q</version>
              <scope>compile</scope>
            </dependency>
            ...
          </dependencies>

      %h3 Previous releases

      %p All previous releases can be downloaded from <a href="https://bintray.com/netty/downloads/netty/">here</a>.

      %h3 Nightly builds

      %p Nightly builds can be found at <a href="http://clinker.netty.io/jenkins/job/netty-oraclejdk7/">our CI server</a>. You can also pull the latest snapshots from <a href="http://clinker.netty.io/nexus/content/repositories/snapshots/io/netty/">our Maven snapshot repository</a>.

